e from distinct regions along the path an FRB\npropagates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Apr 2018 18:00:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 Jun 2018 23:44:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-01"}
