nks between\nJamison and Kazhdan sets in $\\mathbb{Z}$ are exhibited, and many examples are\ngiven.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Apr 2018 12:17:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-05"}
