llowed by cosmological data constraints, and more negative values of $w$\ngive positive kinetic energy for non-zero values of $\\xi$. Also, our results\nare generally applicable for a massive free field or a field with a small\npotential in a 0th- or 1st-order FLRW background dominated by a fluid with a\nconstant $w$. [abridged]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Apr 2018 16:42:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Sep 2018 19:47:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-12"}
